Most Software Product has to deal with COne of Cone of Uncertainty.

As late as you react the to the disaster, Althought you're gonna get acurate pression of the Disaster but the Cost of the Project goes high.
So If the problem is found at the Beginning and project change is made at the Beginning, it will be less expensive.
But when you are at the end of delivering the  product, then changes to be made will be difficult and will be expensive.